A configurable terminal presentation tool.

INSTALLATION
------------

	git clone https://github.com/krzysckh/prez
	cd prez
	make
	sudo make install

CONFIGURATION
-------------

~/.config/prez/prez.cfg

Syntax:

option (tab) value

Configuration options:

option		values		description
-----------------------------------------------------------
padding		int (0-50)	set padding for text
		(in chars)
image_handler	/path/to/prg	set image handler
				(read HANDLERS section)
markup_handler	prez | markdown	set text handler
				so prez can use other syntax
title_handler	prez | 		set a title handler
		/path/to/prg	(read HANDLERS section)
color_handler	prez |		set a color handler
		/path/to/prg	(read HANDLERS section)

